Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.62,0:00:02.37,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I, Kamijyo Touma,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:07.48,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,came in contact with a homeless shrine maiden, who, *quote* calls herself a magician *end quote*.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.56,0:00:12.91,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Together with another magician called Stiyl, I headed to where this shrine maiden was being held captive...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.73,0:00:15.56,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...and what I saw there was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:18.29,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:26.65,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,500)\pos(1158,493)}#08 Ars Magna\NThe Alchemy of God
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.22,0:00:27.17,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,A corpse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:31.32,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably from the Thirteen Knights of the Roman Catholic Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:33.74,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,From the looks of this, they were probably completely annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:35.30,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:37.31,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,We're on a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.31,0:00:40.58,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,What's so surprising about a corpse or two lying around?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:43.42,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't anyone shocked or panicking?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:46.38,Default,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi, long day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:49.61,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:53.47,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,The difference between the "outerside" and the "innerside".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:56.71,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,These students are inhabitants of the outerside of the coin;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:02.56,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,they won't be able to notice us enemies from outside that are on the innerside of the coin right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:06.40,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Neither can we, in any way, interfere with their actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:11.65,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:15.89,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Without destroying the core of the magic, you won't be able to dispel this seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:19.51,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the core is somewhere outside, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:27.97,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I have one more reason to fight now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:40.37,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, couldn't we have taken the elevator?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.98,0:01:42.90,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,We're on the innerside of the coin,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:45.41,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,so we won't be able to press buttons that are on the outerside of the coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:48.79,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about phones?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:49.98,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:55.44,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you know, I was wondering if I could call from the innerside of the coin to the outerside of the coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:01:58.53,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,See for yourself, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:00.66,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:10.66,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, th-this is Index Libro-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:12.46,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, this is Kamijyo speaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:13.47,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Um, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:18.19,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What, is this the first time you've answered a phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:18.86,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:21.74,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this is Touma's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:26.72,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,And Touma, for you to be using something as exaggerated, excessive, cumbersome,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:29.02,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,and unfriendly as a phone, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:30.77,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:34.47,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there were two lasagnas in the refrigerator,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:35.50,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,was that-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:36.78,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Did you eat them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:39.99,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there was pudding in the refrigerator-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:42.47,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...What... Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:43.87,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...Did you eat it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:44.77,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You ate it, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:45.81,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You ate it, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:47.98,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:50.97,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I can reach you by phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:52.32,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hanging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:54.63,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:57.94,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that your life is shortened a day for every minute you speak on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:06.09,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:07.33,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:09.67,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought you might be too relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:15.26,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,I said we were on a battlefield,\Nyet you're chatting nonchalantly with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:19.19,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, I don't care if you die because of your conceitedness,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:21.59,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,and in fact, I'd be jumping for joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:24.69,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,but heck, just don't drag me down because that's problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:25.87,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:30.58,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:34.06,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a target of romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:36.34,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,You should be well aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:43.61,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, her body was one that would die unless her memories were erased in one year periods.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:48.64,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Many people were in the position you're in right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:52.92,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,To become her father, her sibling, her friend, her teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.86,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Many people wished to become different roles for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:04:00.78,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,You have succeeded in what I failed to do in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:03.34,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:07.70,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only difference between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:11.68,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:14.67,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The one that saved Index isn't me, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:17.66,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The one that Index desires is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.65,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...me, before I lost my memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:32.11,Default,girl,0000,0000,0000,,And that was so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:33.23,Default,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:43.58,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've seen the science religion,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:44.78,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,but this seems pretty normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:49.51,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,I'd think they have a portrait of the religion's founder framed somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.32,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It does seem pretty safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.01,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.59,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:05.80,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,because there's no way people on the outerside of the coin can see people like us on the innerside of the coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:08.24,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The wings of the seraph shine brightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:11.70,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The bright light is a pure white color that reveals sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:14.16,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The pure white color is the mark of purity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.58,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The mark is the result of one's actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:18.05,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}One's actions represent the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:19.15,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The future is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:21.35,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Time is uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:21.90,Default-alt,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Auto-warning, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.88,Default-alt,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,These students that were supposed to be on the outerside of the coin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:28.64,Default-alt,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,...have been put on the innerside of the coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.30,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uniformity is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.88,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}All is created by the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.27,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The past is the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:28.90,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}There is but one cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:30.32,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}One is sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:31.54,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sins are humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:34.50,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Humans fear, and fear is guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:36.96,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Guilt rests within oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:41.02,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If there is something one despises within,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:44.81,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}the wings of the seraph will reveal your sins,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:47.22,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and force it from within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:52.79,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Imagine Breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.02,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,You're up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:55.73,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:57.50,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:06.71,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:10.52,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Your right hand was able\Nto fend off a Dragon Breath attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:13.91,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,So you must be nuts to be showing your back right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:16.13,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear that from someone using me as a shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:17.97,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,There's just too many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:20.45,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,One right hand won't be able to cover them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:22.92,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,But, damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:26.85,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,That may be a replica, but to be able to reproduce Gregorio's Choir...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:29.26,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's that Gregorio whatever?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:37.31,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Originally, it was a grand magic spell that employed 3,333 monks in a cathedral and gathered their prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:40.69,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then, there's no way we can beat that head on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:46.24,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,No, Gregorio's Choir requires the simultaneous control of a large amount of people or else it won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:49.70,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,If we can destroy whatever's synchronizing them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:07:00.60,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I do have a secret plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:02.36,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then use it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.38,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.19,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:11.07,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Bad luck, scarecrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:21.28,Default,girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The flame punishes sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:23.69,Default,girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Purgatory governs the flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:26.94,Default,girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Purgatory was created to burn sinners,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:30.07,Default,girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}as the only violence God recognizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:34.31,Default,girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Violence is the acknowledgment of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:36.71,Default,girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Acknowledgement is recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:37.43,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:40.64,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you see that your own body is in trouble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:39.53,Default,girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Recognition rests within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:40.64,Default,girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Within refers to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:44.46,Default,girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Connect your inner self with the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:03.40,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.65,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:55.45,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,But man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:58.53,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,That alchemist is messed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:02.75,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,The one cutting a path through enemies should be oneself, not others...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:12.40,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, using Gregorio Replica would definitely direct you to the core no matter where it was hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:16.44,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,Inevitably, there were two intruders to begin with, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:20.31,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,Evidently, your familiar has been devoured by Gregorio Replica?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:24.41,Default,Styil,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately for you, that one's much tougher than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:26.74,Default,Styil,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.57,Default,Styil,0000,0000,0000,,What do you intend on doing by luring me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:33.48,Default,Styil,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemist, Aureolus Izzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:38.03,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Treatment suffices.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.21,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:44.54,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Her skin was torn open and her capillaries injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:47.48,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Had her arteries been cut, it would be worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:50.12,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a doctor, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:53.36,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,I am much more informed about\Nthe flow of blood than other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:54.90,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Assist me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:03.81,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, wai-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:04.62,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Do not panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.43,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,That is rude to the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.33,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sphinx.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.59,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Touma go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:18.60,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there was pudding in the refrigerator-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:21.14,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...What... Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.05,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...Did you eat it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:22.99,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You ate it, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:24.06,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You ate it, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.24,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:28.85,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Something's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:33.98,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Touma would just say\N"oh, well" when someone eats his pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.37,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Rune marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.80,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Done for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:56.63,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're... pretty skilled...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:59.88,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a certain famous doctor without a license?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.07,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Not a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:02.92,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.14,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:09.90,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, which part shows that you're a magician?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:11.84,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,I have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:16.21,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:18.80,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,A magic wand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:21.39,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a police club!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:23.12,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,New material.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:24.27,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Quit joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.10,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,We need to call an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:29.04,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.49,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sound as if you're not a part of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:32.79,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You need to go home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:40.45,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That is, stop being held here, so that we can go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:43.08,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,I have my own objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:46.10,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,An objective that does not involve escaping from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:48.31,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,but to achieve something that I can only accomplish while here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:50.02,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:54.52,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,It's more accurate to say that without the alchemist, the objective would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:58.87,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But, a friend wouldn't hold someone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:02.18,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,That was before Aureolus took over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:07.30,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,I do not sense the necessity of going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:11.09,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Going out without caution will just attract "that".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:18.07,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you're saying you've been hiding here all this time just because you don't want to be noticed by vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:20.22,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.51,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what kind of an organism they're like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:25.14,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:28.72,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is different between them and us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:32.88,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,They can laugh, and act for the sake of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.38,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,That's what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:39.00,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,My blood attracts them with its nice smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:42.34,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,I attract them, gather them, and kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:44.14,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,There is no motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:48.43,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,I just kill them without exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:54.26,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Academy City is a place that governs power,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:56.51,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought they would know the secret behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:13:00.44,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,If the secret is known, then the method to remove it might be available...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:04.71,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,But the secret isn't known.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.43,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to kill anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:12.49,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,I have decided that if I had to kill anyone, I would kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:15.30,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.81,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to attract vampires,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:20.94,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,then why were you spending all your money on food outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:22.24,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:26.76,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Aureolus needs me because he wants a vampire sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:32.81,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay inside the seal, then I can't attract vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.24,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:37.25,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the opposite of your objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:39.32,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Aureolus promised me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:41.66,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,...that he wouldn't hurt the vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:43.88,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Aureolus said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:45.82,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,...that there's someone he wants to save...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:48.32,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,...that he needed the powers of a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.12,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the pact was made.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:53.13,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,To use this power not to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:54.79,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,but to save.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:57.75,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:05.61,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If he really were the kind of person you speak of,\Nthen I couldn't let him commit any more wrongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:11.16,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If I let this happen, then it'll really end up being an irreversible mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:17.87,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,Necessarily, what about me leads you to say that this will be irreversible?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:19.85,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:23.07,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,Composedly, it does not matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:24.96,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,I shall come for you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:31.16,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, you have questions I need not answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:33.87,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:36.54,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,You shall not approach me any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:40.88,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:45.51,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,H-How come...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:48.43,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,Disappointingly, you bore me, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:49.68,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,Fade away-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:50.49,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:53.58,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:58.42,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Deep Blood has enough power to kill vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:14:59.54,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:06.42,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,And so at the very end, you ended up leaning on Deep Blood, relying on it, and prayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:09.09,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,What's the difference between you and me, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:11.51,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:14.42,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,This person doesn't know the significance of Deep Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:18.42,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,He came here to rescue someone that he met today and barely knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:21.85,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Aureolus Izzard, what is your objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:27.77,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Is satisfying yourself by killing civilians your objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:31.53,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,If that kind of meaningless act is your objective,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:33.07,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,then I shall quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:38.08,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,I have the right of choosing to bite\Nmy own tongue to end my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:43.44,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,Necessarily, there is no time to waste in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:47.39,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,Young man, do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:48.51,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,I won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.31,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,Forget everything that happened here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:04.38,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:08.49,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Where the mana that was being supplied to\Nthe runes near Touma's room is completely cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:14.16,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:17.86,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,That you're here means we're still in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:22.42,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm forgetting something important...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:23.49,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,...am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:31.70,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's probably something that doesn't need to be remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.45,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:38.46,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,Forget everything that happened here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:55.31,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Let me teach you a charm that will erase your doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:58.71,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Oriental charms are Kanzaki's specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:00.12,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.79,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Just close your eyes and put your tongue out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:12.70,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a souvenir for having the balls to use me as a bait and escaping yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:29.28,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,There's a seal set up to prevent enemy intruders from escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:31.60,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, it has been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:33.56,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:35.06,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:39.53,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, you wouldn't happen to recall the name, Aureolus Izzard?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:43.37,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,No, perhaps that should be a fortunate occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:44.25,Default,Aureolus,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:54.67,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, these guys were the ones at the entrance-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.11,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,The remnants of the Thirteen Knights, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.58,Default,13,0000,0000,0000,,Commence attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.57,0:18:04.50,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Gregorio Choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:08.66,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,The true choir of Gregorio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:14.23,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But, didn't you say a lot of people were required for this Gregorio whatever?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:22.08,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Those 3,333 monks are probably sending their prayers right now from St. Peter's Basilica.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:27.84,Default,13,0000,0000,0000,,Revelation 8:7 -
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:33.00,Default,13,0000,0000,0000,,"When the first angel blew his trumpet, hail and fire were mixed with blood and thrown to the earth"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:38.33,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are they trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:40.29,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Holy magic bombardment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:41.12,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Bombardment?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:45.06,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Himegami and other students are still inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:03.20,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.10,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's rising again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:19.05,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Ars Magna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:21.06,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ars Magna?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.99,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,That is our enemy's,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:27.33,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Aureolus Izzard's true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:48.42,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Sphinx?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:51.23,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:54.04,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...this is Index's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:28.01,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:28.03,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The varied clashes surrounding Index.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:31.01,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The moment the alchemist who rebels against destiny shows his fangs,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:33.07,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,roars will resonate inside the Misawa Cram School.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:35.20,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Deep Blood".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:37.54,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross paths,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:38.89,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,this epic will begin!
